    "name": "Napocalypse",
    "steam_appid": 3220380,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Vesuvius sleeps, but Napoli is awake with monsters. Ten years after a meteorite shattered the sky, its alien energy has twisted the world into a hostile, mutated wilderness. Now, humanity's last survivors rise from the rubble, gifted with strange new powers and an unbreakable will to reclaim their home.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Napocalypse</strong> is a strategic deckbuilding roguelike where you lead a party of survivors through the ruins of Napoli. Navigate the treacherous city map, secure strategic locations, and battle terrifying creatures warped by alien radiation.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🗺 RECLAIM THE CITY, DISTRICT BY DISTRICT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move your party across a sprawling map of Napoli. Every location and landmark you reclaim—from the local <strong>Hospital</strong> to the <strong>National Museum</strong>—grants your party powerful and unique <strong>Perks</strong>. After each victory, you must choose: <strong>search</strong> the area for vital supplies and new survivors, or make <strong>camp</strong> to rest, heal, and prepare for the dangers ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/913653a65c3522365c97c43a6d61c383.poster.avif?t=1768356932\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/913653a65c3522365c97c43a6d61c383.webm?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/913653a65c3522365c97c43a6d61c383.mp4?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🤝 <strong>STRENGTH IN NUMBERS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are not alone in this fight. Find other survivors and decide who braves the dangers of the mutated city. Each character brings a unique set of skills to the table, opening up entirely new strategic possibilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/fe196a5a8e47377ab010843e094833fd.poster.avif?t=1768356932\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/fe196a5a8e47377ab010843e094833fd.webm?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/fe196a5a8e47377ab010843e094833fd.mp4?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⚒️ ARTIFACTS OF POWER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover over 300 powerful <strong>Relics</strong> that can be found throughout the city. The effects of these relics can greatly enhance your deck through powerful interactions and synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/62e09522ffb4c99ab2c9dd162cfb14aa.poster.avif?t=1768356932\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/62e09522ffb4c99ab2c9dd162cfb14aa.webm?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/62e09522ffb4c99ab2c9dd162cfb14aa.mp4?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🃏 EVOLVING CARDS WITH MODIFIERS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget repetitive card plays! Our <strong>Card Modifiers</strong> feature adds exciting new dimensions to your runs. Instead of encountering the same &quot;Cleave&quot; repeatedly, you might find a <strong>&quot;Limitless </strong>Cleave<strong>&quot;</strong> that can be upgraded infinitely, or a <strong>&quot;Mega </strong>Cleave<strong>&quot;</strong> that costs more energy but deals  massive damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/2c575f1d39cbf6f8d071884ba4ab011d.poster.avif?t=1768356932\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/2c575f1d39cbf6f8d071884ba4ab011d.webm?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/2c575f1d39cbf6f8d071884ba4ab011d.mp4?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>⚡ MASTER THE ELEMENTS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield the very forces of nature. Your survivors command ten distinct elements, including Fire, Water, Lightning, and Psychic. Discover devastating elemental reactions to gain the upper hand in combat. Will you <strong>vaporize</strong> Water with Fire, <strong>electro-charge</strong> it with Lightning, or <strong>freeze</strong> it with Ice? Outsmart your foes with tactical synergy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/4ef3544132471d3fb2bcd75aa120e187.poster.avif?t=1768356932\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/4ef3544132471d3fb2bcd75aa120e187.webm?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/4ef3544132471d3fb2bcd75aa120e187.mp4?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌦️ ADAPT TO A DYNAMIC APOCALYPSE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dynamic <strong>Weather System</strong> featuring rain, thunderstorms, heatwaves, and sandstorms will directly impact combat, altering elemental effectiveness and forcing you to adapt your strategies on the fly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/0f3c5cfee033644b15d85036e8d6b017.poster.avif?t=1768356932\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/0f3c5cfee033644b15d85036e8d6b017.webm?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/0f3c5cfee033644b15d85036e8d6b017.mp4?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏴‍☠️ A SHIFTING BATTLEFIELD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mutated horrors are not mindless. Enemy factions led by powerful elite and boss mutants actively command their own territories on the map. As you make your move, they make theirs, spreading their influence and fortifying their positions. Prepare for sudden invasions on secured territory! Will you rally your party to defend your foothold? Or will you make the tactical retreat, forfeiting the location to survive and fight another day?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/dc5fa76011e69cf6b4eed10c27176bde.poster.avif?t=1768356932\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/dc5fa76011e69cf6b4eed10c27176bde.webm?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/dc5fa76011e69cf6b4eed10c27176bde.mp4?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⛺️ <strong>STRATEGIC CAMPING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Safety at camp is temporary and must be used wisely. Use <strong>Food</strong> items to replenish your party's energy, but ration carefully—exhaust your supplies and you risk <strong>Starvation</strong>. With a limited number of actions, every choice counts. Do you use <strong>Medical</strong> supplies to reduce <strong>Stress</strong> and treat <strong>Injuries</strong>, or spend time with <strong>Books</strong> to permanently improve your combat abilities?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/0242bfe5e48eaa57db9da99b28f22f73.poster.avif?t=1768356932\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/0242bfe5e48eaa57db9da99b28f22f73.webm?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/0242bfe5e48eaa57db9da99b28f22f73.mp4?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>☠️ A TRUE ROGUELIKE CHALLENGE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the unforgiving world of <strong>Napocalypse</strong>, death is final. Every choice matters, and every run is uniquely generated with new locations, encounters, and loot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/ebcb7fefb2f7448aa6b9dd664a373fac.poster.avif?t=1768356932\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/ebcb7fefb2f7448aa6b9dd664a373fac.webm?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220380/extras/ebcb7fefb2f7448aa6b9dd664a373fac.mp4?t=1768356932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you lead the survivors to a new dawn, or will Napoli be lost to the rubble forever?</strong> </p>",
